2012-07-04 Release 1.0.1
- Patch release for author in LICENSE and Modulefile.

2012-07-03 Release 1.0.0
- Manage hosts(5) as a single file.
- Drop support for `purge` param.
- Add entry for `ip6-allhosts`.
- Manage FQDN as `127.0.1.1` instead of `$::ipaddress`.
- Warn when `$::fqdn` is not set.
- Apply gds-operations/puppet-module-skeleton standards.
- First release to Forge.

2013-06-27 Release 0.0.1
- Initial release
